Regulatory Class: Class I exempt, meets limitations of exemptions per 862.9 (c)(1)(4)
Regulation Name(s): Urinary protein or albumin (nonquantitative) test system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TPUC3 Total Protein Urine/CSF Gen.3 turbidimetric assay for quantitative determination of total protein in urine and CSF using COBAS Integra 400 plus.
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative determination of total protein in urine and cerebrospinal fluid to aid in diagnosis and treatment of renal, heart, thyroid diseases, meningitis, brain tumors, and central nervous system infections.
